ornament; {#svaBAvasuMdaraM vastu na#} 
{#saMskAramapekzate#} <ls>Dṛ. Ś. 49</ls>; <ls>Ś. 7. 23</ls>;  
<ls>Mu. 2. 10.</ls>

{@--8@} Impression, form,
mould, operation, influence; {#yannave#} 
{#BAjane lagnaH saMskAro nAnyaTA Bavet#}  
<ls>H. Pr. 8</ls>; <ls>Bh. 3. 84.</ls>

